################### README of VTK poject in C++ ######################

##### Installation of VTK #######
I used synaptic who is very simple of use. It is a software who let us to install severall package easily. Here I installed all package of VTK 6.

tape : 
	sudo synaptic

package :
	vtk6
	vtk6-examples
	vtk6-doc
	tcl-vtk6
	python-vtk6
	libvtk6
	libvtk6-java
	libvtk6-dev

To execute some example we will need Cmake too
	
